text: Wolfgard Voss (, Mönning, 24 June 1926 - 7 July 2020), nicknamed "Wölfi", was a German gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. She was born in Oldenburg, Germany. Voß died on 7 July 2020 in Oldenburg, aged 94. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1926 births Category:2020 deaths Category:German gymnasts Category:Olympians for East Germany Category:People from Oldenburg (city)
